						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying near the well in the garden opposite the Vināyaka temple at Chauḷikēri.</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th century.</p>						

						<p>This badly changed record seems to register a gift of land and money, the details of which are all lost. </p>						

